1"><label>&#x02021;</label><p>p &#x0003c; 0.05 vs Losartan</p></fn><fn fn-type="other" id="TF3-2"><label>&#x000a7;</label><p>p &#x0003c; 0.03 vs Ramipril</p></fn></table-wrap-foot></table-wrap>
